
This script will give you the random for the work to make word cloud.

I- REQUIREMENTS

Install matplotlib and python2.7

II- DESCRIPTION

	- simple.py: will generate your text to make word cloud.

III- INPUT

	- test.txt: store your data as text file

IV-OUTPUT

*.png file

V- HOW TO RUN IT

	1. Open terminal and go to your directory.
	2. Launch the script python simple.py
	3. Then you will the result as testwc.png


